  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Bone metabolism is adversely affected by severe burns in children for a period of time.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      More closely monitored biochemical and radiologic parameters of bone and mineral metabolism
      will increase the likelihood of earlier detection of abnormalities and possible therapeutic
      interventions.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
